 Fontaines DC、Kneecap 和 Kim Gordon 领衔 2024 年 AIM 奖提名https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-dc-kneecap-kim-gordon-lead-aim-awards-2024-nominations-3783240?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fontaines-dc-kneecap-kim-戈登领导的 2024 年目标奖提名Liberty DunworthTue, 13 Aug 2024 10:05:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeHip-hopIndiePopRapRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3783240 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Kim Gordon、Fontaines D.C. 和 Kneecap" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今年的其他提名者包括 Barry Can&#39;t Swim、Jorja Smith 和 Ezra Collective</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-dc-kneecap-kim-gordon-lead-aim-awards-2024-nominations-3783240">由 Fontaines DC、Kneecap 和 Kim Gordon 领衔的 2024 年 AIM 奖提名</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Kim Gordon、Fontaines D.C. 和 Kneecap" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kim-Gordon-Fontaines-Kneecap@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2024 年 AIM 奖提名名单已公布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-gordon">Kim Gordon</a>领衔。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/kneecap-film-review-biopic-michael-fassbender-3779661">《膝盖》评论：大胆、勇敢，是有史以来最好的音乐传记片之一</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>独立音乐奖今天（8 月 13 日）揭晓，旨在庆祝英国独立音乐界的成就，并将于 10 月 17 日返回伦敦标志性的 Roundhouse。</p><p> Kim Gordon 凭借她的唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kim-gordon-the-collective-review-lyrics-tracklist-3597930">The Collective</a> 》获得了“最佳独立专辑”奖提名， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Jorja Smith</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jorja-smith-falling-or-flying-review-rb-star-finds-a-joyful-complex-sound-3505079">Falling Or Flying</a> 》以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">Barry Can&#39;t Swim</a>的《When Will We Land?》也获得了提名。名单中还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/d-block-europe">D-Block Europe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mount-kimbie">Mount Kimbie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/actress">Actress</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/antony-and-the-johnsons">ANOHNI and the Johnsons</a> 、Nabihah Iqbal、Nubiyan Twist 和 Skrapz。</p><p>乔贾·史密斯 (Jorja Smith) 还凭借歌曲“Little Things”进入“最佳独立歌曲”提名名单。这里列出的其他人包括 Fontaines DC 的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-share-pummelling-new-single-starburster-and-announce-new-album-romance-3619061">Romance</a> ”主打单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/fontaines-d-c-starbust-track-review-xl-romance-3618968">Starburster</a> ”、Kneecap 的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-and-fontaines-d-c-s-grian-chatten-team-up-for-the-infectious-better-way-to-live-3542385">Better Way To Live</a> ”（他们与 Fontaines 主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grian-chatten">Grian Chatten</a>一起创作）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a>的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-share-fiery-new-single-ajala-and-announce-uk-and-european-tour-3750237">Ajala</a> ”等等。</p><p> CASISDEAD、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> 、Barry Can&#39;t Swim、Saint Harison 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bar-italia">Bar Italia</a>均入围“英国独立突破奖”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lynks">Lynks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/antony-szmierek">Antony Szmierek</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miso-extra">Miso Extra</a> 、OneDa 和 Kitty Amor 均入围“One To Watch”提名类别。 </p><figure id="attachment_3783250" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783250" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783250" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270.jpg" alt="乔贾·史密斯 (Jorja Smith) 将于 2024 年登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Jorja-Smith@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783250" class="wp-caption-text">乔贾·史密斯 (Jorja Smith) 将于 2024 年登台表演。图片来源：Matt Jelonek/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>其他获得提名的类别包括“最佳独立 EP/混音带”、“最佳独立混音”和“最佳独立视频”。</p><p> “最佳现场表演者”奖将再次由全球粉丝评选，公众投票现已<a href="https://independentmusic.typeform.com/to/YufqFy9K" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>开放，其余类别的提名，包括“最佳精品厂牌”和“独立冠军”，将于 2019 年公布。未来几个月。</p><p> “我们希望您和我们一样对 2024 年独立音乐奖第一批提名者名单感到兴奋，”AIM 临时首席执行官 Gee Davy 说道。 “每年，我们的时尚评委小组都会在最喜爱的广播、媒体和在线杂志上评选出一份很棒的名单。今年跨越了英国独立音乐界的地区和国家、流派和社区，表彰成功、才华和艺术。”</p><p> AIM 主席露丝·巴洛 (Ruth Barlow) 补充道：“祝贺今年 AIM 奖的第一批提名者，这些名单让我们对英国独立行业的长度和广度有一个很好的了解，并突显了 AIM 杰出创新者、文化创造者和商业成功者的情况。社区必须提供。”</p><p>迄今为止公布的提名表明，2024 年对于 Ninja Tune 来说是重要的一年，《Actress》、《Barry Can&#39;t Swim》、《Nabihah Iqbal》和《George Riley》等影片均已入围。提名者还包括 EGA Distro、XL Recordings 和 Heavenly Recordings 各三件作品。 </p><figure id="attachment_3783249" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783249" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783249" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270.jpg" alt="爱尔兰嘻哈乐队 Kneecap 的 Mo Chara 和 Móglaí Bap 将于 2024 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kneecap@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783249" class="wp-caption-text"> Mo Chara 和 Móglaí Bap of Kneecap 将于 2024 年演出。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>有关颁奖典礼现场表演的更多细节以及该奖项与 BBC 合作的更多细节将在稍后公布。下面列出了完整的提名者名单。</p><h2